broadwick.graph

Class UndirectedGraph<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • broadwick.graph.UndirectedGraph<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the vertex type.
    E - the edge type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph<V,E>, Serializable

    public class UndirectedGraph<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
extends Object
implements Graph<V,E>
    A DirectedGraph, suitable for sparse graphs, that permits parallel edges..

    The implementation here is backed by the DelegateTree implementation in the JUNG library.

    See Also:
